OL,5, Female pupils say they have been left  
OL,6, "humiliated" over enforcement of a     
OL,7, uniform policy at a Merseyside school. 
OL,9,FGirls have been made to enter Rainford 
OL,10,FHigh School in St Helens separately to 
OL,11,Fboys and have had their skirt length   
OL,12,Finspected by male teachers, they claim.
OL,14,FHundreds of pupils staged a protest    
OL,15,Fagainst how rules, which have left some
OL,16,Fpupils in tears, have been imposed.    
OL,18,FThe school has not commented directly  
OL,19,Fon the inspections but said it has a   
OL,20,F"clear policy" on uniforms in place.   
